snippet.description:
Calmed by the Dark Leviathan is set to release July 2nd on Itchio and November 30th on Steam.
Itchio: https://calmed-by-the-dark-games.itch.io/calmed-by-the-dark-leviathan
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1676260/Calmed_by_the_Dark_Leviathan/

Earth is now ruled by dragons, the last humans live in underground shelters, is up to Europa, Sofia, Claire and Virginia to defy the gods and save the world!

Discover the ending to the Calmed by the Dark saga in our most ambitious game to date, where everything is going to be decided.

 Fight, capture and upgrade giant monsters!
Action combat;
Open World to explore;
Gather resources and use it to repair things or trade with other shelters;
Multiple endings and New Game+;
Enter the sewers and fight against shadow creatures.

